{
  "id": "adv_main_02_10_04",
  "title": "東京編2章24話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_unrest-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……信じられない\n麻奈さんの曲を奪うだなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Unbelievable.\nThey plan on stealing Mana’s songs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.3333333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 6.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。それどころか存在そのものを消そうとしている\nなぜそこまで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Not just that‚ they’re trying to erase her very existence.\nWhy go so far…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 14.4488208453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "私、今までアイドルに悪い人は\nいないって思ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Until now‚ I believed there was\nno such thing as an evil idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9821541786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "たとえ事務所やスタイルが違っても\n根っこでは、同じ目標を持った仲間だって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if we belong to different agencies or have different styles‚\nI thought deep down we were a group sharing the same goals…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7821541786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 26.7488208453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "残念ですけど、スリクスとは\nそんな関係にはなれないでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ but you won’t be able to have\nthat kind of relationship with IIIX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0154877345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 31.5488208453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "トップアイドルは通過点ゆうてたもんなぁ\nうちらとは何もかもが違う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For them‚ becoming top idols is just a checkpoint.\nThey’re different from us in every way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2488208453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 37.8821541786
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "そんな考え方の人達が\nファンをちゃんと見てるとは、私には思えません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I doubt that people like that\nreally even care about their fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2821541786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 44.2821541786
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "いくら歌がうまくたって、ダンスが出来たって……\nそんなのって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how good they are at singing or dancing‚\nit doesn’t matter…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.015487512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 49.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "分かるよ、みんなファンに希望を届けたくて\n頑張って歌っているんだもんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. You’re all singing with everything you’ve got\nto bring hope to your fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5300519233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 55.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私達は沢山のファンに\n歌を通じて希望を届け続けたいと思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. We want to keep bringing hope\nto as many fans as possible through our songs!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 62.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……スリクスと姫野さんの思惑がどうであれ\n私達の目標は変わりません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whatever IIIX and Ms. Himeno’s intentions may be‚\nour goal remains the same.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 69.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "私達は、I-UNITYに優勝して\nBIG4に並ぶトップアイドルになります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We will win I-UNITY\nand become top idols that rival the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 75.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、スリクスはうちらがきっちり倒すわぁ\n長瀬麻奈にも、星見プロにも手は出させません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In other words‚ we’ll make sure to take down IIIX.\nWe won’t let them touch Mana Nagase or Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 83.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、だから、みんなは安心して下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. So you don’t have anything to worry about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 87.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEがスリクスを下せば\nBIG4への道が一気に開かれます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If TRINITYAiLE defeats IIIX‚\nour path to the BIG4 will open before us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "そうすれば、姫野さんだって\n私達の意見を無視は出来ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ even Ms. Himeno\nwon’t be able to ignore what we have to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 98.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "……瑠依ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 100.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……君達は、また星見プロを\n守ろうとしてくれているのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you girls trying to protect\nHoshimi Productions again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 104.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "勘違いしないで下さい\n私達は自分達が正しいと信じた道を進むだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t get the wrong idea.\nWe’re just following the path we believe is right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8764.607238799996,
          "startTime": 115.9646072388
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "これで全て伝えました\n失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve said everything we came to say.\nso excuse me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2866.666666600011,
          "startTime": 117.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 116.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、待って！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui‚ wait!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tears-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 119.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hall",
      "startTime": 119.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_04-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "……さくら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1,
